title: Fantasy Extravaganza: QBs and philosophies
itunes:title: Fantasy Extravaganza: QBs and philosophies
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down the recent rash of injuries and give their take on notable quarterback battles. Then, the heroes finish off the Fantasy Extravaganza talking undervalued and overvalued quarterbacks and their draft philosophies.
